SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c00767033
Version: 1

HPSBMA02149 SSRT050968 rev.1 - HP OpenView Operations, 
Remote Unauthorized Access and Denial of Service (DoS)

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as soon as possible.

Release Date: 2006-09-12
Last Updated: 2006-09-12

Potential Security Impact: Remote unauthorized access and Denial of Service (DoS)

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified in HP OpenView Operations. 
This potential vulnerability could be exploited remotely to allow unauthorized access 
or to create a Denial of Service (DoS).

References: CVE-2002-0392

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
OpenView Operations 7.1, 8.0, 8.1,
OpenView Operations for Windows a.07.21, a.07.20, a.07.10, a.07.00

BACKGROUND

AFFECTED VERSIONS

HP-UX B.11.00
HP-UX B.11.11
===========
OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-LIN-CLT
action: install PHSS_32380 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-UX11-CLT
action: install PHSS_32423 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-AIX-CLT
action: install PHSS_33252 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-UXIA-CLT
action: install PHSS_33253 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-SOL-CLT
action: install PHSS_33256 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-OSF-CLT
action: install PHSS_33257 or subsequent

OVOPC-CLT.OVOPC-NT-CLT
action: install PHSS_33280 or subsequent

END AFFECTED VERSIONS
RESOLUTION

HP has made the following patches available to resolve the issue. 
The patches can be downloaded from http://itrc.hp.com

Each patch is to be installed on the operating system listed in the 
"System to be Patched" column. Each patch is for communication 
with the operating system listed in the "Client System" column.

Patch                         System to be     Client
(or subsequent)          Patched             System
 ----------------------------------------------------------
ITOSOL_00394            Solaris                 HP-UX PA
ITOSOL_00395            Solaris                 Linux
ITOSOL_00431            Solaris                 AIX
ITOSOL_00432            Solaris                 HP-UX IA
ITOSOL_00435            Solaris                 Solaris
ITOSOL_00436            Solaris                 HP Tru64 UNIX
ITOSOL_00437            Solaris                 Windows

OVOW_00162              Windows              Linux
OVOW_00163              Windows              HP-UX PA
OVOW_00179              Windows              AIX
OVOW_00180              Windows              HP-UX IA
OVOW_00181              Windows              Solaris
OVOW_00182              Windows              HP Tru64 UNIX
OVOW_00190              Windows              Windows
OVOW_00194              Windows              Windows

PHSS_32380                HP-UX PA             Linux
PHSS_32423                HP-UX PA             HP-UX PA
PHSS_33252                HP-UX PA             AIX
PHSS_33253                HP-UX PA             HP-UX IA
PHSS_33256                HP-UX PA             Solaris
PHSS_33257                HP-UX PA             HP Tru64 UNIX
PHSS_33280                HP-UX PA             Windows

MANUAL ACTIONS: No

